title: Goin Down to South Park
description:
A mockumentary which covers the making of the show South Park in a fictional fashion, apparently spoofing similar such shows, with the creators pretending to be arrogant, obnoxious jerks who are only in it for the money. This documentary is featured on the Complete Second Season DVD set for South Park, released in 2003.

This is a downloaded copy from Youtube, still in the five uploaded parts. Looks fine though. I didn't see a version of it here previously so I went looking.
